    "usage_count": 0,
    "audio_url": "/segments/SEG-SEED-00035-T1/audio.wav",
    "script_text": "Hot take from Onay — R&B peaked in the early 2010s. The production, the vulnerability, the melodies? We haven't topped that era yet. I said what I said."
